  <div class="modal-content">
    <span class="close" id="closeModalBtn">&times;</span>
    <h2>Quick-Reference Cheat Sheet</h2>
    <table>
      <tr><th>Action</th><th>Points</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Tap your own color word</td><td>+5</td><td>You have 25 chances</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Tap another‚Äôs color word</td><td>+10 (double)</td><td>75 chances (steals)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Steal a turn</td><td>+20</td><td>Opponent times out (5 sec), you get 2 sec to tap</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Skip a word (Next)</td><td>-5</td><td>Word returns to shuffle</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Failed steal (voted out)</td><td>-10</td><td>Lose points if group rejects steal</td></tr>
    </table>
    <h3>üé§ Snappy Tutorial</h3>
    <p>
      ‚ÄúWelcome to the Ultimate Music Word Showdown! Here‚Äôs how you play:<br><br>
      You‚Äôre competing solo against up to 3 other players, taking turns through 10 rounds each.<br><br>
      Tap words in your own color to score 5 points. See a chance to steal from someone else? Tap their color word fast and earn double points‚Äî10 points!<br><br>
      If an opponent freezes for more than 5 seconds, you‚Äôve got 2 seconds to tap and steal their turn. Pull it off and you snag a 20-point bonus!<br><br>
      But skip a word? That‚Äôll cost you 5 points, and the word goes right back into the mix. Try to avoid getting voted out for a bad steal ‚Äî that‚Äôll lose you 10 points!<br><br>
      Keep your eyes sharp, your fingers faster, and climb that leaderboard. Ready? Let‚Äôs play!‚Äù
    </p>
